xwikidoc.content: [[image:ShlekGnarl.png||style="float: right;"]]Shlek Gnarl is a priest of Jerok who also happens to be one of the wererats living in [[Under Tisloch>>doc:UnderTisloch]]. He serves as Skikker's main advisor. He will fight fiercely if his charges are attacked but is otherwise simply a more powerful and clever wererat with certain priest powers.
